About Me

I am a Data Analyst/Scientist skilled in SQL, Python, Tableau, Power BI, Machine Learning and Statistics.Hope you dig it :)

Hello, I'm Dev Jindani, a Master of Science in Information Systems student at Syracuse University with a strong GPA of 3.8. I hold a Bachelor of Engineering in Information Technology from Thakur College of Engineering & Technology, Mumbai, with a GPA of 3.7.

My educational journey has equipped me with a robust foundation in data analysis, and my technical skills reflect my passion for this field. Proficient in programming languages such as Python, C++, Java, and SQL, I have a deep understanding of data analysis tools, including RStudio and libraries like Pandas and NumPy. I excel in data visualization using tools like Tableau and can effectively mine, clean, and analyze data to derive valuable insights. My experience with databases, web technologies, and machine learning, as well as my expertise in statistical analysis and Excel, enable me to make data-driven decisions. Thank you for visiting!
